sql_query.sql: SELECT "users".* FROM "users" INNER JOIN "user_emails" ON "user_emails"."user_id" = "users"."id" WHERE "users"."staged" = TRUE AND (lower(user_emails.email) IN ('staged@account.com')) ORDER BY "users"."id" ASC LIMIT 1
SELECT "user_custom_fields"."name", "user_custom_fields"."value" FROM "user_custom_fields" WHERE "user_custom_fields"."user_id" = 1080 ORDER BY id asc

SELECT "user_emails"."id", "user_emails"."user_id", "user_emails"."email", "user_emails"."primary", "user_emails"."created_at", "user_emails"."updated_at" FROM "user_emails" WHERE "user_emails"."user_id" = 1080 AND "user_emails"."primary" = TRUE LIMIT 1
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "user_emails" WHERE "user_emails"."primary" = TRUE AND "user_emails"."id" != 1081 AND "user_emails"."user_id" = 1080 LIMIT 1
